1 SECTION 7. Prosecutions for offenses committed before the effective date of this
2 act are not abated or affected by this act, and the statutes that would be applicable but for this act
3 remain applicable to those prosecutions.
4 SECTION 8. This act becomes effective December 1, 2025, and applies to offenses
5 committed on or after that date.
